\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e736be5fdee5b80114c0de1352e19a7bbf1e6653","tid":82220,"uid":70922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"世間上最厚顏無恥莫過於猁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ac0617ff9d9ccab49245f9ebc7414e25669f49","tid":82220,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T20:20:20.000Z","msg":"車狗死返入狗竇啦雙紅會關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"0476231f8770151e8dfad42acd53cf3528481aa7","tid":82220,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T20:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單刀拉衫 都唔紅 第一日睇波？</blockquote><br />\n有，佩奧爾vs洛賓，出動到360度交剪腳重要拉哂衫咁，吹都唔吹"},{"pid":"cf9cb2befaedd1cf7d28da4045f8645790f52fd6","tid":82220,"uid":25651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T20:42:00.000Z","msg":"49000執返一分咋 戰勝你老母咩"},{"pid":"c28ca8946f939810b3828315316ede417be3fcac","tid":82220,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T20:48:54.000Z","msg":"起碼冇越位先出聲啦垃圾"},{"pid":"8ddd09066545ca2cd5861e78b5a84153fe90fec8","tid":82220,"uid":20224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T21:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單刀拉衫 都唔紅 第一日睇波？</blockquote><br />\n屌你乜人嚟咖，車利都幫"}]}